      },
      "date": "2015-06-15 18:24:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: -Code-Review\n\nInitial results indicate that 12603 addresses the LU-4300 like deadlock that appeared after the LU-6390 patch was installed. The customer installed 12603 two days ago and has not seen the deadlock since. They had been hitting it quite often so this is a positive sign. But they don't have a known reproducer so I thought I'd let them run with the patch for a couple of more days before declaring success. But I have no objections to the LU-6390 patch landing.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
